Main Component
* 500 Tenderloin beef
* 50 gram rice flour
* 30 gram tapioca flour 
* 1000ml Water, to boil with Beef
* 600-1000ml Beef Stock result OR use beef stock 1000ml
* Cooking Oil

Grounded Paste:
- [x] 1/2 sdt garam
- [x] 1/2 sdt merica utuh, [sangrai]
- [x] 1 sdt jintan, sangrai
- [x] 1 sdm ketumbar, [sangrai]
- [x] 1/2 jari kunyit, [Sangrai] OR 1/4 sdt Bubuk kunyit
- [x] 1 ruas/ 1 cm Jahe, cincang
- [x] 4 butir Kemiri [Sangrai]
- [x] 6 clove garlic
- [x] 10 Pieces small shallot
- [x] 9 Cabe Merah Keriting 

Bumbu Cemplung
- [x] Chicken Stock Powder, to taste.
- [x] Grounded white pepper, to taste.
- [x] Salt, to taste. 
- [x] 1 Sdm Asam Kandis
- [x] 2 pieces of lemongrass
- [x] 3 Bay leaves 
- [x] 5 Kaffir Lime leavs
- [x] 2-3 pieces of clove
- [x] 6 AUS Curry leave
- [x] 2 cm Lengkuas/ Galanga (Repeat)
- [x] 2 pieces Cardamon OR 1/4 sdt bubuk cardamon
- [x] 2 cm Cinnamon
- [x] 1 Star Anise 
- [x] 2.5 sdt gula pasir

Instructions:
1. Sangrai the ingredient with [Sangrai] sign.
2. Ground the spices, with 100ml water. Grind until fine
3. Tumis grounded paste pake minyak goreng sampe wangi
4. Masukin sapi, masak setengah mateng kemudian potong kecil2
5. Masukin ke dalam panci dan tambah air.
6. Rebus sapi + bumbu Cemplung
7. Saring bumbu sisakan air
8. Kentalkan pake rice flour sampe consistency nya benar

To visualize the cooking method better, refer to this video https://youtu.be/h1VlrMOdbc8

